msgid ""
"The probability density function (PDF), usually denoted as f(x), is a "
"function of a random variable X.\n"
"    The value of f(x) provides the relative likelihood that a realization of "
"the random variable X yields a value equal to x.\n"
"    More formally, the PDF is defined as a derivative of a cumulative "
"distribution function (CDF).\n"
"\n"
"    The density plot displays the probability density function of a random "
"variable.\n"
"    The <i>y</i>-axis displays the value of the density function for a "
"particular value of the random variable (displayed on the <i>x</i>-axis)."
msgstr ""
"Fungsi kepadatan probabilitas (PDF), yang biasa dinotasikan sebagai f(x), "
"adalah fungsi dari variabel acak X.\n"
"    Nilai f(x) memberikan kemungkinan relatif bahwa realisasi variabel acak "
"X menghasilkan nilai yang sama dengan x.\n"
"    Secara lebih formal, PDF didefinisikan sebagai turunan dari fungsi "
"distribusi kumulatif (CDF).\n"
"\n"
"    Plot densitas menampilkan fungsi kepadatan probabilitas dari suatu "
"variabel acak.\n"
"    Sumbu <i>y</i> menampilkan nilai fungsi densitas untuk nilai tertentu "
"dari variabel acak (yang ditampilkan pada sumbu <i>x</i>)."

msgid ""
"The probability mass function (PMF), usually denoted as f(x), is a function "
"of a random variable X.\n"
"    The value of f(x) provides the probability that a realization of the "
"random variable X yields a value equal to x.\n"
"\n"
"    The probability mass plot displays the probability mass function of a "
"random variable.\n"
"    The <i>y</i>-axis displays the value of the probability mass function "
"for a particular value of the random variable (displayed on the <i>x</i>-"
"axis)."
msgstr ""
"Fungsi massa probabilitas (PMF), yang biasa dinotasikan sebagai f(x), adalah "
"fungsi dari variabel acak X.\n"
"    Nilai f(x) memberikan probabilitas bahwa realisasi variabel acak X "
"menghasilkan nilai yang sama dengan x.\n"
"\n"
"    Plot massa probabilitas menampilkan fungsi massa probabilitas dari suatu "
"variabel acak.\n"
"    Sumbu <i>y</i> menampilkan nilai fungsi massa probabilitas untuk nilai "
"tertentu dari variabel acak (yang ditampilkan pada sumbu <i>x</i>)."

msgid ""
"The cumulative distribution function (CDF), usually denoted as F(x), is a "
"function of a random variable X.\n"
"    The value of F(x) provides the probability that a realization of the "
"random variable X yields a value that is equal to or smaller than x.\n"
"\n"
"    The cumulative probability plot displays the cumulative distribution "
"function of a random variable.\n"
"    The <i>y</i>-axis displays the value of the cumulative distribution "
"function for a particular value of the random variable (displayed on the "
"<i>x</i>-axis)."
msgstr ""
"Fungsi distribusi kumulatif (CDF), yang biasa dinotasikan sebagai F(x), "
"adalah fungsi dari variabel acak X.\n"
"    Nilai F(x) memberikan probabilitas bahwa realisasi variabel acak X "
"menghasilkan nilai yang sama dengan atau lebih kecil dari x.\n"
"\n"
"    Plot probabilitas kumulatif menampilkan fungsi distribusi kumulatif dari "
"suatu variabel acak.\n"
"    Sumbu <i>y</i> menampilkan nilai fungsi distribusi kumulatif untuk nilai "
"tertentu dari variabel acak (yang ditampilkan pada sumbu <i>x</i>)."

msgid ""
"The quantile function, usually denoted as Q(p), is the inverse of the "
"cumulative distribution function.\n"
"    The function gives the quantile such that the probability of the random "
"variable being less than or equal to that value equals the given probability "
"p.\n"
"\n"
"    The quantile plot displays the quantile function.\n"
"    The <i>y</i>-axis displays the quantile of which the probability that "
"the random variable is less or equal to that value is equal to p (displayed "
"on the <i>x</i>-axis)."
msgstr ""
"Fungsi kuantil, yang biasa dinotasikan sebagai Q(p), adalah invers dari "
"fungsi distribusi kumulatif.\n"
"    Fungsi ini memberikan kuantil sedemikian rupa sehingga probabilitas "
"variabel acak yang kurang dari atau sama dengan nilai tersebut sama dengan "
"probabilitas p yang diberikan.\n"
"\n"
"    Plot kuantil menampilkan fungsi kuantil.\n"
"    Sumbu <i>y</i> menampilkan kuantil yang probabilitas variabel acak "
"kurang dari atau sama dengan nilai tersebut adalah p (yang ditampilkan pada "
"sumbu <i>x</i>)."

msgid ""
"<h3> Demonstration of the %1$s </h3>\n"
"This demonstration is divided into four parts.\n"
"The first part displays the %2$s, its probability density function, "
"cumulative distribution function, and quantile function.\n"
"The second part allows you to generate data from the %3$s, compute "
"descriptive statistics, and display descriptive plots.\n"
"The third part allows you to estimate the parameters of the %4$s.\n"
"The fourth part allows you to check the fit of the %5$s to the data.\n"
"\n"
"<b>References</b>\n"
"\n"
"Blitzstein, J. K., & Hwang, J. (2014). <i>Introduction to probability.</i> "
"Chapman and Hall/CRC.\n"
"\n"
"Leemis, L. M., & Pasupathy, R. (2019). The ties that bind. <i>Significance, "
"16</i>(4), 8–9.\n"
"\n"
"For relationships with other distributions, visit %6$s.\n"
"\n"
"%7$s"
msgstr ""
"<h3> Demonstrasi %1$s </h3>\n"
"Demonstrasi ini dibagi menjadi empat bagian.\n"
"Bagian pertama menampilkan %2$s, fungsi kepadatan probabilitas, fungsi "
"distribusi kumulatif, dan fungsi kuantilnya.\n"
"Bagian kedua memungkinkan Anda membangkitkan data dari %3$s, menghitung "
"statistik deskriptif, dan menampilkan plot deskriptif.\n"
"Bagian ketiga memungkinkan Anda mengestimasi parameter dari %4$s.\n"
"Bagian keempat memungkinkan Anda memeriksa kecocokan %5$s terhadap data.\n"
"\n"
"<b>Referensi</b>\n"
"\n"
"Blitzstein, J. K., & Hwang, J. (2014). <i>Introduction to probability.</i> "
"Chapman and Hall/CRC.\n"
"\n"
"Leemis, L. M., & Pasupathy, R. (2019). The ties that bind. <i>Significance, "
"16</i>(4), 8–9.\n"
"\n"
"Untuk hubungan dengan distribusi lain, kunjungi %6$s.\n"
"\n"
"%7$s"

